    "title": "מִזְמוֹר שִׁיר לְיוֹם הַנִיצָּחוֹן | A Song for Victory Day, a psalm anticipating Death's end by Aryeh Baruch",
    "author": "Aryeh Baruch",
    "coauthors": [
